parameters:
It's been two weeks since I used the potent magic,
and I haven't had an erection.

It's not just that the magic consumption is high.
There were too many flaws.

I can't satisfy my friends with benefits like
this.

However, there is a solution. If we apply the
Theory of Tohelena, surely...
Masamune Is the magic... not complete?
Skeleton Head That shouldn't be possible...

[Leon] But there is a solution using the Theory of
Tohelena, right?

Masamune What is that theory... I've never heard
of it.

[Skeleton Head] Please be complete... It wouldn't
make sense if it causes ED.

[Skeleton Head] My friends with benefits will be
sad.
Skeleton Head, do you know something?
